{
    "type": "fix",
    "subject": "Fix Os family type detection",
    "body": "The Os class now correctly determines whether the executing OS matches the set OS family type. The setFamily method has been updated to set the family type in lowercase and the eval method has been updated to compare the OS name in lowercase. This change ensures that the Os class works correctly regardless of the case of the OS family type."
}

