    "subject": "Fix exception message in ExecTask",
    "body": "The exception message in the runExec method of ExecTask has been updated to include the exception's toString() value. This change aims to provide more detailed information about the exception that occurred during the execution of the task. The method summaries for the runExec method remain unchanged, as the functionality and implementation details of the method have not been modified."
}

{
    "type": "fix",
    "subject": "Fixed DTDLocation iteration in XMLValidateTask",
    "body": "This commit fixes the iteration over DTD locations in the XMLValidateTask class. The code change is a simple loop iteration fix, where the size of the DTD locations list is now used instead of getting the size in each iteration. This change improves the code readability and maintainability."
}

{
    "type": "fix",
    "subject": "Fix date formatting in DateUtilsTest",
    "body": "This commit fixes the date formatting in the DateUtilsTest class. The testDateISO method was modified to correctly format a date in ISO 8601 format. The changes ensure that the date formatting function correctly formats a date in ISO 8601 format from a given calendar date."
}

