    "body": "This commit adds the getPendingTasks method to ColumnFamilyStoreMBean, allowing users to retrieve the estimated number of tasks pending for a column family. The method is implemented by returning the queue length of the memtableLock. This feature is part of the CASSANDRA-173 issue, which aims to add atomic counters to track pending tasks. The commit also includes changes to ColumnFamilyStore.java to support the new method."
}

