    "body": "This commit fixes the `doCleanupCompaction` method in `CompactionManager` to correctly remove unnecessary SSTables. The method now compacts SSTables, removes tombstones, and updates secondary indexes. The changes improve the overall performance and efficiency of the compaction process."
