    "body": "This commit fixes the inconsistency in the thread pool name of CommitLogArchiver, which was previously named 'commitlog_archiver' but is now renamed to 'CommitLogArchiver' to match the naming convention of other thread pools. This change is a minor fix to ensure consistency in the naming of thread pools, and it may require updates in any monitoring applications that rely on the old name."
}

{
    "type": "fix",
