    "type": "fix",
    "subject": "Fixed lazy loading and ordering for application certificates in Client class",
    "body": "This commit fixes the lazy loading and ordering for the application certificates in the Client class. The getApplicationCertificates() method now returns a list of strings representing application certificates, which are stored in a lazy-loaded collection. The changes also include the addition of the @Lob annotation to the applicationCertificates field, which specifies that the collection should be eagerly fetched when the object is loaded."
}

